Dear Student,

SOFTEC 2026, FAST-NUCES Lahore's flagship technology festival, is here!
We invite you to participate in this year's AI Hackathon — one of the
most competitive and rewarding student competitions in Pakistan.

Competition Details:
- Event: AI Hackathon – SOFTEC 2026
- Venue: FAST-NUCES, Lahore Campus
- Date: May 3-4, 2026
- Prize Pool: PKR 500,000 (1st: 250k, 2nd: 150k, 3rd: 100k)
- Team Size: 2-4 members

Problem Statement Theme: "AI for Student Productivity"

Eligibility:
- Enrolled undergraduate or postgraduate student
- Valid student ID required on day of event
- Open to all universities in Pakistan

Registration Requirements:
- Team registration form (all members required)
- University enrollment certificates
- 1-page project idea pitch (submitted online)

Registration Deadline: April 25, 2026

Register your team: https://softec.nu.edu.pk/hackathon/register
Event brochure: https://softec.nu.edu.pk/brochure-2026.pdf
Contact: softec@nu.edu.pk | Instagram: @softec_fast

We look forward to seeing your innovative solutions!

SOFTEC Organizing Committee
FAST-NUCES Lahore
